Related to my smelting concept in gen. discussion.

[code]public void oreSmelting(int ore1, int ore2, int bar, int xp) {
			c.closeInterface();
	if (c.playerHasItem(ore1, 1) && c.playerHasItem(ore2, 1)) {
			c.deleteItem(ore1, 1);
			c.deleteItem(ore2, 1);
			c.addItem(bar, 1);
			c.sM("You make a bar.");
			c.setAnimation(899);
			c.addSkillXP(xp, 13);
		}	
	}[/code]
